adept.serialization

Class JSONSerializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • adept.serialization.AbstractSerializer
      • adept.serialization.JSONSerializer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISerializer

    public class JSONSerializer
extends AbstractSerializer
implements ISerializer
    JSON serializer. We use the XStream library for XML with an additional JettisonMappedDriver to serialize and deserialize into and from JSON as well.
